Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:07.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a sickness that continues to \Nprogress without any visible symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:11.74,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,there was someone hiding \Nin our town of Morioh,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.16,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,committing murders somewhere in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:22.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems like no one's even realized \Nthat these murders are taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.83,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's such shocking and chilling information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:31.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,But there is currently no \Nway of finding that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:37.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know how many Stand \Nusers currently live in Morioh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:42.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,And rather than worry about a huge problem \Nthat presents no visible symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.94,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,people are worried about what \Nthey should have for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.61,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,because that's what's right in front of us.
